<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-1077] application/xml to application/json is not properly converting </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-1077</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I am using simple proxy to convert application/xml to application/json with latest build &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;proxy name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;echoService&quot;&lt;/span&gt; xmlns=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;http:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//ws.apache.org/ns/synapse&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
&lt;/span&gt;    &amp;lt;target&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;inSequence&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;property name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;messageType&quot;&lt;/span&gt; value=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;application/json&quot;&lt;/span&gt; scope=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;axis2&quot;&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;log level=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;full&quot;&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;respond /&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;/inSequence&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;outSequence&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;send /&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;/outSequence&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;/target&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;publishWSDL uri=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;file:repository/conf/sample/resources/proxy/sample_proxy_1.wsdl&quot;&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/proxy&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the input payload is &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;a&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;b&amp;gt;c&amp;lt;/b&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;and expected output is&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;{
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;a&quot;&lt;/span&gt;: { &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;b&quot;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;c&quot;&lt;/span&gt; }
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However the out come was &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;{&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;a&quot;&lt;/span&gt;:{&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;$&quot;&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;\n\n&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;b&quot;&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;c&quot;&lt;/span&gt;}}

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;=============================&lt;br/&gt;
I have tested the very simple xml &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt; &amp;lt;a&amp;gt;b&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;and the outcome was as expected.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;{&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;a&quot;&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;b&quot;&lt;/span&gt;}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/Synapse%20-%20Trunk/5306/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/Synapse%20-%20Trunk/5306/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
